    {"city": "Helsinki", "country": "FI", "status": "Nordic-expansion", "data_quality": "good_via_Fintraffic"}
  ],

  "known_gaps": [
    "Live regulation data (servicedagar, ptillaten records) requires API key from Trafikkontoret",
    "Per-zone pricing is not in open data; must come from operators or scraping parkering.stockholm",
    "Real-time spot occupancy is not exposed by Trafikkontoret as open data",
    "Residential permit holders are personally identifiable and never published",
    "Operator zone-ID mappings (EasyPark's zone X = which Stockholm Zone polygon) require partnership or scraping",
    "Private-land Kontrollavgift parking has no central registry; coverage is fragmented per landlord",
    "Sign images linked to LTF data: not currently provided; must be photographed or sourced separately"
  ]
